text:
Possibly the best thing about "AI Art" it that is accustoms an entire generation to the idea that "reality" itself is an infinite latent space out which multimodal experiences are generated in spacetime, based on the intention of the animal observer.

"In reality time and space exist in you; you do not exist in them." - Sri Nisargadatta Maharaj

"The universe is simply the spatial/temporal logic of the animal observer" - Robert Lanza
